handsome /ˈhændsəm/

1. ADJ A handsome man has an attractive face with regular features. 英俊的 

例： ...a tall, dark, handsome sheep farmer. …一位高个、皮肤黝黑、相貌英俊的牧羊人。 

2. ADJ A handsome sum of money is a large or generous amount. (款项) 相当大的; 可观的 [正式] [ADJ n] 

例： They will make a handsome profit on the property. 他们将从地产中赚取一笔可观的利润。

